Laravel 11 New Features
=================================

Laravel 11 was updated in March-May 2024


Features
================

1) Min. Version PHP 8.2

2) Maintenance Mode :-

You can enable or disable maintenance mode on your live website.

>> php artisan down : Enable
>> php artisan up : Disable (Website will start working)

3) Health Check Route :- We can check performance report of our website.

website.com/up/

4) once() method - If same method is called again and again, the result is stored in Cache.

function sum()
{
   echo "This is sum function";
}
sum(); // This is sum function --- Store - Cache
sum(); // Result (Cache) : This is sum function
sum(); // Result (Cache) :This is sum function
sum(); // Result (Cache) :This is sum function
sum(); // Result (Cache) :This is sum function
sum(); // Result (Cache) :This is sum function

>> No Resources are used
>> Time consuming
>> Fast
>> Better Performance

5) Default Database : SQLite 

6) New Artisan commands

php artisan make:class ClassName -> New Class
php artisan make:enum ENum -> Enum Class
php artisan make:interface Interface -> Interface Class

